            <title>[LU-6419] Fld client lookup should retry another target if  the current target is deactive</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6419</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In fld_client_lookup(), if it fails because the remote target is deactive, it should try another target, instead of return error, which might cause the application failure. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
